          .wolf-item.is-caption.is-caption--left(data-speed="-1")
            .wolf-item-inner
                p.figcaption I've actually developed this site twice. After finishing the first round, Success Academy was rebranded by Pentagram and asked Makeable to redesign the site a second time to reflect the new branding. We took what we learned the first time and made it much better the second time.
